+    public TIntVector() {
+        super();
+    }
+
+    public TIntVector(TIntVector other) {
+        super(other);
+    }
+
+    /**
+     * Get element value

+     * @param index element index
+     * @return element value
+     */

+

+     * @return this

+    public abstract int[] getIndices();
+

+     * @param delta update value
+     * @return this

+
+    /**

+     *

+     * @return this
+     */

+
+    @Override
